WEBVTT

00:20.800 --> 00:21.640
Ms. Fan.

00:25.440 --> 00:26.480
I agree.

00:27.080 --> 00:28.200
Then drink it while it's warm.

00:28.720 --> 00:30.120
What I mean is…

00:30.880 --> 00:32.159
about marrying into your family.

00:32.840 --> 00:33.880
I agree.

00:41.400 --> 00:42.280
Good.

00:43.800 --> 00:44.640
Good.

00:46.360 --> 00:48.280
Once we bow before the hall and wed,

00:48.360 --> 00:49.760
we'll tell the world you've married in.

00:51.000 --> 00:53.600
When the house deed is transferred
and the money flows again,

00:53.680 --> 00:56.480
I'll hire the finest physician in town.

00:56.560 --> 00:57.480
The best medicine there is.

00:57.560 --> 00:58.760
When you're healed,

00:58.840 --> 01:00.640
whether you stay or go
will be your choice.

01:00.720 --> 01:03.320
And you're not worried that once I leave,

01:04.160 --> 01:06.200
your uncle will come back
to seize the house?

01:09.240 --> 01:11.600
With the deed in my name,
he can't threaten me.

01:11.680 --> 01:14.480
Besides, if you do leave,

01:14.560 --> 01:16.720
I'll simply say you had
urgent matters elsewhere.

01:16.800 --> 01:18.160
Who would know otherwise?

01:19.760 --> 01:21.200
You've really thought this through.

01:23.680 --> 01:24.680
And if you decide to stay,

01:25.400 --> 01:26.320
I'll provide for you.

01:28.440 --> 01:29.280
Why?

01:29.360 --> 01:31.200
You may not realize this,

01:31.280 --> 01:33.960
but butchers earn quite well.

01:35.480 --> 01:36.600
That's not what I meant.

01:38.160 --> 01:40.960
If I were left crippled,
you'd still keep me?

01:41.040 --> 01:41.880
For what?

01:41.960 --> 01:43.200
Because you're good-looking.

01:44.800 --> 01:46.400
<i>Fan Changyu,</i>

01:46.480 --> 01:49.360
<i>how could you just blurt that out?</i>

01:51.120 --> 01:55.040
There are handsome men
everywhere in this world.

01:56.160 --> 01:59.240
-I…
-But I carried you out of the snow.

02:01.880 --> 02:04.040
If, once you recover,
you have nowhere to go--

02:04.120 --> 02:07.080
When I am well, I will take my leave.

02:08.120 --> 02:09.400
I will not overstay my welcome.

02:16.000 --> 02:16.840
Very well.

02:18.960 --> 02:20.160
I'll be going.

02:23.840 --> 02:24.720
Ms. Fan.

02:27.240 --> 02:28.320
I will repay you someday

02:29.320 --> 02:30.160
for saving my life.

02:30.960 --> 02:32.800
If there is anything you desire,

02:33.960 --> 02:34.880
name it.

02:36.680 --> 02:38.720
I have no grand desire.

02:39.920 --> 02:42.640
You agreeing to a marriage in name only
and helping me keep my home

02:42.720 --> 02:44.000
is already more than enough.

02:44.080 --> 02:47.200
This arrangement is merely repayment
for shelter.

02:48.840 --> 02:52.200
If you have a wish, think bigger.

02:53.440 --> 02:55.440
A wish…

02:57.080 --> 02:58.560
Bigger…

03:00.080 --> 03:01.360
Then I will think bigger.

03:02.240 --> 03:05.600
I want to rebuild my father's pig pens.

03:05.680 --> 03:07.640
Fence off a larger plot of land.

03:08.160 --> 03:10.120
Raise 20 or 30 pigs!

03:14.720 --> 03:17.600
You may think even bigger.

03:17.680 --> 03:18.760
Then 100.

03:20.800 --> 03:22.120
I meant

03:23.040 --> 03:24.760
something beyond pigs.

03:24.840 --> 03:27.880
One hundred pigs would fetch
over a hundred taels of silver.

03:28.480 --> 03:30.240
Is that not grand enough?

03:30.320 --> 03:32.240
Then… 200.

03:33.080 --> 03:35.560
Wait. I'd never finish slaughtering them.

03:38.280 --> 03:39.120
I see now.

03:42.800 --> 03:43.640
Let's seal it.

03:53.840 --> 03:55.480
-Good day, Changyu.
-Good day, Changyu.

03:55.560 --> 03:56.640
Good day.

04:03.680 --> 04:04.840
‎Look, there's more!

04:04.920 --> 04:07.080
Changyu!

04:07.160 --> 04:10.200
Changyu!

04:10.280 --> 04:11.320
Run along now.

04:11.840 --> 04:13.120
So pretty.

04:20.640 --> 04:21.680
Ready.

04:21.760 --> 04:22.840
All right.

04:22.920 --> 04:23.760
One, two.

04:23.840 --> 04:25.000
Thank you, miss.

04:27.560 --> 04:28.840
That'll do. Here.

04:30.360 --> 04:31.720
-Mrs. Wang.
-Changyu.

04:31.800 --> 04:32.720
Ms. Wang. Ms. Zhang.

04:32.800 --> 04:37.600
WANG'S BRAISED MEATS
ELEGANT EMBROIDERY HOUSE

04:40.760 --> 04:41.600
<i>Madam.</i>

04:42.600 --> 04:46.640
My mother once stored fabric here
for my wedding robes.

04:47.920 --> 04:49.440
-Come this way.
-Thank you.

04:55.760 --> 04:57.880
Yes, there is fabric reserved.

04:57.960 --> 05:01.280
Just enough for one full bridal set.

05:01.960 --> 05:03.880
Can it be made
into a groom's robe instead?

05:03.960 --> 05:05.840
A groom's robe?

05:06.760 --> 05:09.040
I thought that voice sounds familiar.

05:09.120 --> 05:10.880
Isn't that our Changyu?

05:10.960 --> 05:12.400
Mrs. Chen.

05:12.480 --> 05:15.440
I heard from Mrs. Zhao
you are joining the wedding rush.

05:15.520 --> 05:17.440
When's the auspicious day?

05:17.520 --> 05:18.880
Seven days from now.

05:19.400 --> 05:21.000
You're only ordering wedding clothes now?

05:21.080 --> 05:22.120
That may be cutting it close.

05:22.720 --> 05:24.480
Since word of conscription
in Chongzhou spread,

05:24.560 --> 05:26.840
everyone planning to wed is scrambling.

05:26.920 --> 05:29.200
All hoping to leave an heir
before the draft.

05:29.280 --> 05:31.560
My shop hands can barely keep up.

05:34.720 --> 05:37.480
Mrs. Zhao said
the groom is quite handsome.

05:39.120 --> 05:40.360
I suppose so.

05:40.440 --> 05:41.280
At least I'm not at a loss.

05:42.720 --> 05:44.800
Mrs. Chen, please hurry the work.

05:44.880 --> 05:46.600
I'll pay extra.

05:46.680 --> 05:48.240
I'm not asking you for extra silver.

05:48.320 --> 05:49.600
Don't worry.

05:49.680 --> 05:52.680
I helped your mother choose
that wedding fabric and kept it here.

05:53.280 --> 05:55.200
She longed to see you married.

05:58.600 --> 05:59.960
Mrs. Zhao also said

06:00.040 --> 06:03.320
the groom is some distant relation
from Chongzhou.

06:09.240 --> 06:10.480
Since he's from Chongzhou,

06:11.680 --> 06:14.480
does he know
whether Marquis Wu'an truly fell?

06:15.880 --> 06:16.920
Marquis Wu'an is dead?

06:17.640 --> 06:19.480
-Are you sure?
-Marquis Wu'an?

06:20.080 --> 06:21.760
That's what people have been saying.

06:21.840 --> 06:23.160
Marquis Wu'an is dead.

06:23.240 --> 06:24.680
Dead in Chongzhou, not even bones left.

06:24.760 --> 06:25.680
Just like his father.

06:25.760 --> 06:26.920
Nonsense!

06:27.000 --> 06:28.040
How could he be dead?

06:28.120 --> 06:29.720
I'll smash your teeth in!

06:29.800 --> 06:31.360
-Should I give him another?
-Beat him!

06:31.440 --> 06:32.680
-Beat him!
-Beat him!

06:44.200 --> 06:45.840
HALL OF EXALTED VIRTUE

06:45.920 --> 06:49.760
<i>Dayin has faced Northern Jue</i>
<i>on the battlefield for years.</i>

06:49.840 --> 06:53.040
Marquis Wu'an, Xie Zheng,
a hero of his age,

06:53.120 --> 06:55.200
now fallen without even remains to bury.

06:55.280 --> 06:57.280
This is a wound to the realm.

06:58.480 --> 07:02.040
I intend to posthumously confer upon him
the title Duke Yizhong.

07:02.120 --> 07:02.800
EMPEROR QI MIN OF DAYIN

07:02.880 --> 07:05.440
Grant the Xie army 1,000 taels of gold.

07:06.160 --> 07:08.400
What say my ministers?

07:13.440 --> 07:14.720
Your Majesty is wise.

07:14.800 --> 07:17.680
Marquis Wu'an guarded
the vital northwest passes.

07:17.760 --> 07:18.680
Peerless in valor.

07:18.760 --> 07:21.280
In over a century of our dynasty,

07:21.360 --> 07:25.320
only Xie Zheng has borne that title.

07:25.400 --> 07:28.680
To now elevate him as Duke Yizhong

07:28.760 --> 07:31.440
reveals Your Majesty's boundless virtue.

07:31.520 --> 07:33.640
A blessing for the people.

07:33.720 --> 07:39.240
In his youth, he led troops
to wash away the shame of Jinzhou.

07:39.320 --> 07:42.160
The Northern Jue trembled at his name.

07:42.240 --> 07:44.640
Our generals will gladly
lay down their lives

07:44.720 --> 07:46.760
to repay Your Majesty's grace.

07:46.840 --> 07:48.600
I concur.

07:48.680 --> 07:51.400
Very well. Issue my decree.

07:51.480 --> 07:52.600
Court is adjourned for three days.

07:52.680 --> 07:54.920
We shall don plain garments
and hold mourning rites.

07:55.000 --> 07:57.960
Let the entire realm grieve.

07:58.480 --> 08:00.920
We obey.

08:01.000 --> 08:03.720
Your Majesty, I arrived late.

08:28.800 --> 08:30.800
Though you're unwell, Chancellor Wei,

08:30.880 --> 08:32.400
you still attend court.

08:32.480 --> 08:34.400
A blessing for Dayin.

08:35.360 --> 08:36.320
Bring him a seat.

08:43.679 --> 08:45.240
CHANCELLOR WEI YAN OF DAYIN

08:45.320 --> 08:46.760
Where were we?

08:48.120 --> 08:51.440
I intend to confer upon Xie Zheng
the title Duke Yizhong,

08:51.520 --> 08:53.200
reward the Xie army with 1,000 taels,

08:53.280 --> 08:54.800
and declare national mourning.

08:56.480 --> 08:58.400
Chancellor Wei, your view?

09:00.880 --> 09:02.720
Marquis Wu'an did achieve great merit.

09:03.400 --> 09:06.320
However, this concerns
the situation at the front.

09:06.400 --> 09:09.000
If the entire nation enters mourning,

09:09.080 --> 09:12.280
it may dampen the army's morale.

09:12.360 --> 09:16.560
At that moment, Northern Jue
and the forces of Prince Changxin

09:16.640 --> 09:18.960
may seize the advantage.

09:26.360 --> 09:27.320
Chancellor,

09:27.960 --> 09:31.080
Marquis Wu'an died in the prime of life
for this country.

09:31.720 --> 09:34.720
His Majesty's act is born
of mercy for an untimely death,

09:35.240 --> 09:37.680
a true mark of his sacred benevolence.

09:38.560 --> 09:44.200
Though some scholars
criticize his slaughter at Jinzhou,

09:44.280 --> 09:46.160
when weighing merit against fault,

09:46.240 --> 09:48.600
his merit far outweighs his excesses.

09:49.320 --> 09:53.560
To reward him now
demonstrates clear judgment.

09:53.640 --> 09:55.520
It will rally hearts.

09:56.040 --> 09:59.760
How could it weaken the army?

10:01.640 --> 10:04.240
Word has it Marquis Wu'an fell in battle.

10:04.320 --> 10:06.240
Yet to this day, no body has been found.

10:06.920 --> 10:08.640
I chose not to report it.

10:08.720 --> 10:11.080
To mislead the enemy.

10:11.760 --> 10:14.280
As long as his death
is not officially announced,

10:14.800 --> 10:17.000
the enemy cannot be certain.

10:17.920 --> 10:20.000
They will not dare move lightly.

10:21.240 --> 10:25.440
Grand Tutor Li, you may excel
at divining His Majesty's intentions,

10:26.120 --> 10:28.720
but in matters of warfare and strategy,

10:28.800 --> 10:31.600
you would do well to study further.

10:42.600 --> 10:44.880
You are ever deliberate, Chancellor Wei.

10:46.040 --> 10:48.960
I stand corrected.

10:50.400 --> 10:51.720
Chancellor Wei.

10:57.760 --> 10:59.920
Chancellor Wei,
please accept my condolences.

11:01.320 --> 11:02.680
You are most thoughtful, Grand Tutor.

11:04.720 --> 11:08.080
Now that Marquis Wu'an
no longer holds Yanzhou,

11:09.040 --> 11:12.400
who will command the Yanzhou army?

11:15.640 --> 11:19.040
The Yanzhou army serves Great Yin.

11:19.120 --> 11:22.960
Any capable man of court
may be sent there.

11:23.960 --> 11:27.120
Yanzhou guards the frontier.

11:27.200 --> 11:28.680
It must not be mishandled.

11:33.160 --> 11:35.200
Since you've already planned it out,

11:35.280 --> 11:37.080
I needn't have worried.

11:38.480 --> 11:39.560
I shall take my leave.

11:49.320 --> 11:51.800
The old fox shows such concern
for the northwest.

11:51.880 --> 11:55.000
He must be angling
to meddle in border command.

11:59.840 --> 12:02.640
-Has Xie Zheng's body been recovered?
-Not yet.

12:05.160 --> 12:06.400
Any word from the young lord

12:06.480 --> 12:09.520
regarding Marquis Wu'an's disappearance?

12:10.120 --> 12:10.960
None.

12:11.560 --> 12:14.120
That day, we were too close
to He Jingyuan's territory.

12:14.960 --> 12:16.600
We dared not alert him.

12:17.760 --> 12:19.720
I have dispatched men
to continue the search in secret.

12:20.360 --> 12:21.840
Send more.

12:21.920 --> 12:23.560
-Urge them to act swiftly.
-Yes.

12:23.640 --> 12:26.880
His fate must be confirmed.

12:26.960 --> 12:29.400
But more crucial still is that token.

12:29.480 --> 12:31.560
-Yes.
-Inform the Xuan-ranked agents.

12:32.760 --> 12:33.920
If they fail to find it,

12:34.720 --> 12:36.720
-they are not to return.
-Understood.

14:02.800 --> 14:07.040
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL <i>ZHU YU</i>
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

14:11.080 --> 14:12.160
Go away!

14:13.280 --> 14:14.280
Go!

14:14.920 --> 14:15.840
Go!

14:16.680 --> 14:17.920
Stay back! Go!

14:18.720 --> 14:19.920
Go!

14:21.880 --> 14:23.400
Go away! Go!

14:24.760 --> 14:26.000
Go away!

14:29.840 --> 14:31.000
<i>Where did this wolf come from?</i>

14:31.760 --> 14:33.240
<i>It nearly took my hair ribbon.</i>

14:37.720 --> 14:38.880
<i>Where's my shoe?</i>

15:09.000 --> 15:11.080
This young lady truly
does not fear the cold.

15:11.720 --> 15:12.920
In such heavy snow,

15:13.000 --> 15:14.360
walking barefoot on the road.

15:28.520 --> 15:30.480
Something must have happened to her.

15:30.560 --> 15:32.480
Ask where she lives. Give her a ride.

15:34.320 --> 15:35.440
Miss.

15:38.160 --> 15:40.120
My master sees you struggle in this snow.

15:40.200 --> 15:41.600
He would like to offer you a ride.

15:41.680 --> 15:42.720
Where is your home?

15:44.000 --> 15:45.360
That won't be necessary. Thank you.

15:48.840 --> 15:49.920
Miss, please wait.

16:02.400 --> 16:04.320
My surname is Li. I mean you no harm.

16:04.920 --> 16:07.280
You'll ruin your feet
walking barefoot in this weather.

16:07.360 --> 16:08.720
Allow us to take you home.

16:13.520 --> 16:14.960
Then I thank you, sir.

16:24.480 --> 16:25.560
You're most kind.

16:40.080 --> 16:41.280
But you're sitting in the cold.

16:41.960 --> 16:43.520
I feel bad.

16:44.120 --> 16:45.000
Think nothing of it.

16:45.080 --> 16:47.000
Your stockings are soaked.
Warm yourself first.

16:47.600 --> 16:50.280
I've sat inside long enough.
I needed some air.

17:03.120 --> 17:05.599
Changyu, you're home already?

17:06.119 --> 17:07.400
Changyu.

17:07.480 --> 17:09.560
What… What happened to you?

17:10.960 --> 17:12.520
Ran into a wolf on the road.

17:12.599 --> 17:13.839
Lost a shoe escaping.

17:14.359 --> 17:16.400
Luckily these two gentlemen
brought me back.

17:16.480 --> 17:17.319
It was nothing.

17:18.400 --> 17:20.079
Thank you both.

17:20.599 --> 17:22.960
It's freezing out.
Please come inside and warm yourselves.

17:23.040 --> 17:23.920
Madam,

17:24.000 --> 17:25.520
let Ms. Fan change her shoes first.

17:26.040 --> 17:27.160
We have pressing matters.

17:27.240 --> 17:28.319
We must take our leave.

17:28.880 --> 17:30.320
Then thank you, Master Li.

17:33.000 --> 17:33.960
Forgive the trouble.

17:34.520 --> 17:35.560
Gentlemen, wait.

17:35.640 --> 17:37.600
These chestnuts were just roasted.

17:37.680 --> 17:39.760
-Let me pack some for you.
-No need.

17:39.840 --> 17:42.440
Her roasted chestnuts are the finest!

17:42.520 --> 17:43.360
They truly are.

17:43.960 --> 17:45.320
Do take some for the road.

17:45.400 --> 17:47.400
Then we shall accept with thanks.
Much obliged, madam.

17:47.480 --> 17:49.280
-All right, wait here a moment.
-Madam…

17:51.840 --> 17:52.800
Why did you do that?

17:52.880 --> 17:55.680
This is simply how villagers
show gratitude.

17:55.760 --> 17:57.480
We must blend in with them.

17:58.040 --> 17:59.680
It makes your investigation smoother.

17:59.760 --> 18:00.600
Does it not?

18:01.760 --> 18:03.880
Just admit you wanted chestnuts.

18:22.080 --> 18:23.440
<i>I saw nothing.</i>

18:27.720 --> 18:28.560
Come in.

18:35.240 --> 18:36.080
I… I…

18:36.160 --> 18:40.040
I went to Mrs. Chen's to arrange
the wedding clothes today.

18:40.120 --> 18:42.360
Then I realized I forgot
to take your measurements.

18:44.640 --> 18:45.480
Come inside.

19:11.360 --> 19:13.400
You look slender,

19:14.200 --> 19:16.200
but your shoulders are broad.

19:17.040 --> 19:18.080
Like my father's.

19:18.600 --> 19:20.200
Shoulders, one chi eight.

19:34.040 --> 19:35.440
Waist, two chi one.

19:38.160 --> 19:39.720
Leg length, three chi seven.

19:43.240 --> 19:44.480
What is it?

19:45.000 --> 19:46.240
Nothing.

19:46.320 --> 19:47.760
A wolf chased me this morning.

19:47.840 --> 19:49.080
I may have twisted my ankle.

19:50.200 --> 19:51.640
Sit. Let me see it.

19:51.720 --> 19:52.640
No need.

19:53.240 --> 19:54.960
Mr. Zhao will return shortly.

19:55.040 --> 19:56.640
I'll apply some medicine myself.

20:02.560 --> 20:04.600
Sit. Let me look at it.

20:04.680 --> 20:05.800
Before it aches again tonight.

20:09.240 --> 20:11.040
-Is it good?
-It's delicious.

20:18.800 --> 20:19.880
For reasons unknown,

20:20.400 --> 20:22.520
those mysterious men stopped
once they reached Lin'an.

20:28.520 --> 20:30.120
After that, they vanished entirely.

20:30.640 --> 20:33.840
Shall I speak to the local magistrate?

20:36.160 --> 20:38.800
Teacher specifically instructed
that this must remain private.

20:45.720 --> 20:46.800
My lord,

20:46.880 --> 20:49.400
you've searched night after night
for Marquis Wu'an

20:49.480 --> 20:50.400
and still no word.

20:51.320 --> 20:52.720
If you ask me,

20:52.800 --> 20:56.800
it's hardly rare for bodies to vanish
in times of war.

20:57.400 --> 20:58.520
I cannot believe

20:59.880 --> 21:01.600
Marquis Wu'an would fall so easily.

21:04.480 --> 21:06.560
If those men lingered
and did not withdraw,

21:07.760 --> 21:09.600
then Marquis Wu'an must be in Lin'an.

21:16.080 --> 21:17.200
It's dislocated.

21:18.080 --> 21:19.680
Ah! That hurts!

21:19.760 --> 21:20.880
Of course it hurts.

21:21.480 --> 21:23.760
I thought it was only a sprain.

21:24.600 --> 21:25.440
Bear it.

21:30.240 --> 21:31.400
There.

21:40.600 --> 21:41.760
My lord,

21:42.320 --> 21:43.720
fresh-roasted chestnuts.

21:43.800 --> 21:44.880
Still hot.

21:44.960 --> 21:45.800
Eat while they're warm.

21:45.880 --> 21:47.400
-Thank you, madam.
-Madam,

21:48.240 --> 21:50.880
just now, I heard Ms. Fan
cry out upstairs.

21:50.960 --> 21:51.920
Is something wrong?

21:52.560 --> 21:54.640
That's Changyu's husband.

21:55.240 --> 21:57.280
Young couple,
probably just teasing each other.

21:57.360 --> 21:58.440
Her husband?

22:00.320 --> 22:02.160
Why did he not come down to receive her?

22:03.040 --> 22:04.120
He's injured.

22:04.200 --> 22:05.280
Not fit to move about.

22:07.240 --> 22:09.240
-Good, isn't it?
-Very good, madam.

22:10.200 --> 22:12.120
The northwest is in chaos.

22:12.200 --> 22:13.040
I've heard

22:13.120 --> 22:15.280
many wounded refugees from Chongzhou
have married locals

22:15.360 --> 22:16.360
to gain residency.

22:17.280 --> 22:18.760
Ms. Fan's husband

22:19.360 --> 22:20.680
isn't from Chongzhou, is he?

22:24.840 --> 22:27.920
He's a distant kinsman of mine.
From Yanzhou.

22:28.960 --> 22:29.800
Yanzhou.

22:35.560 --> 22:36.760
It's truly better.

22:37.640 --> 22:38.520
It doesn't hurt at all.

22:43.400 --> 22:45.480
I told you to slow down.
Now look, you're choking.

22:46.080 --> 22:48.360
Madam, might I trouble you for some tea?

22:48.440 --> 22:49.320
Of course.

22:49.920 --> 22:52.520
I was so focused on food,
I forgot about drink. Please.

22:53.120 --> 22:54.560
-Come in for some tea.
-Thank you.

23:02.120 --> 23:03.280
Are there guests downstairs?

23:04.000 --> 23:04.840
Oh no.

23:04.920 --> 23:06.800
I left our two benefactors waiting below.

23:12.240 --> 23:14.200
Forgive the humble tea. Please make do.

23:15.240 --> 23:16.720
Ms. Fan was just married?

23:20.360 --> 23:21.440
Well…

23:22.000 --> 23:23.160
He's married into my family.

23:24.560 --> 23:25.400
Married in?

23:26.680 --> 23:28.840
Poor child.

23:28.920 --> 23:31.320
He only just arrived from Yanzhou,

23:31.400 --> 23:32.360
ran into bandits,

23:32.440 --> 23:34.360
was robbed and injured.

23:35.000 --> 23:36.640
Fortunately, Changyu took him in.

23:36.720 --> 23:39.720
She even slaughtered a pig to sell
for his medical fees.

23:41.320 --> 23:42.440
Slaughtered a pig?

23:44.560 --> 23:46.280
Changyu is formidable.

23:47.280 --> 23:49.280
One slap and the pig drops.

23:50.240 --> 23:51.440
She's joking.

23:56.880 --> 23:58.240
Ms. Fan is truly righteous.

23:58.320 --> 23:59.360
Indeed, righteous.

24:04.320 --> 24:05.640
No need to escort us farther.

24:06.520 --> 24:07.360
Here.

24:08.800 --> 24:09.680
Take care.

24:14.200 --> 24:15.120
My lord,

24:15.800 --> 24:18.240
I fear we are chasing shadows.

24:18.840 --> 24:21.600
Marquis Wu'an once refused
even a princess.

24:21.680 --> 24:24.040
Would such a man
marry into a butcher's household

24:24.120 --> 24:25.480
and reset her ankle?

24:26.680 --> 24:28.240
Perhaps I have overreached.

24:28.320 --> 24:30.240
You have not slept in days over this.

24:30.320 --> 24:32.640
Rest on the journey back to Jizhou.

24:32.720 --> 24:33.560
Leave the rest to me.

24:35.240 --> 24:36.160
Let's go.

24:50.600 --> 24:52.160
<i>A carriage from Jizhou.</i>

24:52.920 --> 24:54.240
<i>He Jingyuan's people.</i>

25:00.720 --> 25:02.840
What measurements did I take
for Yan Zheng?

25:12.680 --> 25:14.040
Shoulders…

25:17.000 --> 25:18.520
one chi eight.

25:19.720 --> 25:22.720
Waist, two chi one.

25:25.080 --> 25:25.920
Leg length,

25:27.200 --> 25:28.800
three chi seven.

25:39.240 --> 25:41.160
Yan Zheng.

25:42.760 --> 25:44.080
<i>Yan Zheng…</i>

25:49.240 --> 25:52.360
YAN ZHENG

26:04.880 --> 26:07.040
XIE ZHENG

26:10.240 --> 26:11.400
<i>What is she doing?</i>

26:12.480 --> 26:14.080
<i>Has she found out?</i>

26:26.000 --> 26:26.840
Who is it?

26:27.800 --> 26:28.880
It's me.

26:29.480 --> 26:31.160
I need to speak with you.

26:34.480 --> 26:35.320
Come in.

26:50.920 --> 26:53.040
I've memorized your measurements.

26:53.680 --> 26:55.000
I'll send them to the tailor.

27:07.160 --> 27:09.280
Could you stay up a little longer tonight?

27:09.920 --> 27:11.320
Wait for me. I need you.

27:15.080 --> 27:17.440
There's something we must do together.

27:23.720 --> 27:24.800
Together?

27:25.640 --> 27:26.960
You're a man. I'm a woman.

27:27.480 --> 27:29.000
I cannot do it alone.

27:40.800 --> 27:42.280
That seems improper.

27:43.320 --> 27:45.600
You're about to marry into my family.
What's the harm?

27:46.120 --> 27:46.960
It's settled.

27:57.560 --> 27:59.800
Mr. and Mrs. Zhao must not know.

27:59.880 --> 28:00.760
Keep this between us.

28:14.720 --> 28:15.760
Hurry.

28:15.840 --> 28:17.120
They'll close the gates soon.

28:18.520 --> 28:19.680
Come on.

28:43.040 --> 28:43.960
What is it you want me to do?

28:44.560 --> 28:46.600
Careful. Don't let anyone see. Follow me.

28:56.000 --> 28:57.000
On your knees.

29:05.560 --> 29:07.320
This is the matter

29:08.120 --> 29:09.760
we were to handle together?

29:12.200 --> 29:13.440
My mother said

29:13.520 --> 29:15.920
if you visit a grave at midnight,
you must bring a man.

29:16.960 --> 29:18.200
A man brimming with vigor.

29:19.000 --> 29:20.000
That is you.

29:25.480 --> 29:27.680
MARQUIS WU'AN XIE ZHENG

29:34.560 --> 29:37.880
<i>So that is why</i>
<i>she was writing in the sand earlier.</i>

29:40.080 --> 29:41.840
The authorities have issued
no mourning decree.

29:41.920 --> 29:44.280
Private offerings could invite trouble.

29:45.000 --> 29:46.960
Midnight is safest.

29:47.560 --> 29:49.000
And this spirit tablet…

29:51.760 --> 29:54.000
When you were coughing blood so violently,

29:54.080 --> 29:55.480
I thought you would not survive.

29:56.520 --> 29:57.680
So I carved it for you.

30:00.000 --> 30:01.120
Thank you.

30:01.200 --> 30:03.280
There's no need.
It was never used in the end.

30:06.240 --> 30:08.000
Marquis Wu'an fell on the battlefield.

30:08.880 --> 30:10.560
I meant to set up a spirit tablet for him.

30:11.160 --> 30:14.240
Turns out your name
could be altered a little and still pass.

30:15.680 --> 30:16.560
Yes.

30:17.320 --> 30:18.200
It worked out perfectly.

30:20.200 --> 30:22.040
Huanghuali wood too.
No reason to waste it.

30:24.120 --> 30:27.120
By the way. You fled from Chongzhou.

30:27.200 --> 30:29.560
Do you know how Marquis Wu'an died?

30:30.640 --> 30:31.640
I don't.

30:34.880 --> 30:37.120
You're not kin to him.

30:37.960 --> 30:39.600
Why honor him with a tablet?

30:40.320 --> 30:44.520
Isn't the common talk
that Marquis Wu'an was bloodthirsty,

30:44.600 --> 30:45.880
a demon who butchered cities?

30:46.640 --> 30:47.800
Nonsense.

30:48.960 --> 30:50.080
My father said

30:50.600 --> 30:54.400
he led the army
and retook Jinzhou from Northern Jue.

30:54.480 --> 30:56.040
He avenged his father

30:57.200 --> 30:58.720
and avenged Dayin.

30:59.560 --> 31:00.800
As for slaughtering a city,

31:01.840 --> 31:02.960
if the enemy could do it,

31:04.120 --> 31:05.760
why couldn't he?

31:14.120 --> 31:15.320
You truly think that?

31:17.080 --> 31:19.040
My father used to say,

31:19.120 --> 31:20.960
in 200 years of Dayin,

31:21.040 --> 31:22.720
how many Marquis Wu'ans have there been?

31:23.760 --> 31:25.560
He reclaimed Jinzhou.

31:27.280 --> 31:28.640
The 12 Liaodong prefectures,

31:29.480 --> 31:32.960
lost through decades of war
and countless fallen generals,

31:33.040 --> 31:34.280
were restored by him.

31:35.600 --> 31:37.480
The scholars of today

31:39.200 --> 31:40.640
all condemn him for Jinzhou.

31:41.680 --> 31:42.840
Those learned men

31:43.440 --> 31:44.880
call him ruthless and cruel.

31:45.840 --> 31:47.080
But 16 years ago,

31:47.600 --> 31:49.760
the soldiers and common folk
who died in Jinzhou,

31:50.280 --> 31:51.480
were they not innocent?

31:52.400 --> 31:53.880
Old General Xie died standing,

31:53.960 --> 31:55.240
so he might keep his dignity.

31:55.320 --> 31:57.240
The Northern Jue
disemboweled him and left his body

31:57.320 --> 32:00.400
hanging on the city wall.
He was Marquis Wu'an's father!

32:03.720 --> 32:06.120
To avenge one's father is only right.

32:06.880 --> 32:08.000
Without Marquis Wu'an,

32:08.600 --> 32:09.640
who else

32:10.360 --> 32:12.040
could have held the northwest?

32:16.800 --> 32:18.160
Why are you looking at me like that?

32:18.760 --> 32:19.760
Am I wrong?

32:22.320 --> 32:23.920
You've quite the nerve.

32:28.000 --> 32:28.840
It's just you and me.

32:29.440 --> 32:30.600
That's why I dare speak.

32:42.440 --> 32:43.720
Marquis Wu'an above,

32:44.320 --> 32:45.760
this humble woman, Fan Changyu,

32:46.320 --> 32:48.640
together with my husband Yan Zheng,
have come to see you off.

32:52.520 --> 32:53.840
If your spirit lingers,

32:54.680 --> 32:55.960
watch over the people of Great Yin.

32:56.040 --> 32:57.360
Grant them peace and safety.

32:59.120 --> 33:00.320
And if you meet my parents,

33:04.160 --> 33:05.840
please give them my regards.

33:16.560 --> 33:18.000
If you have a wish,

33:18.080 --> 33:20.040
kneel and speak it.

33:22.080 --> 33:24.440
He gave his life for the nation.

33:24.520 --> 33:26.000
You lose nothing by bowing.

33:50.200 --> 33:52.280
May the fog clear soon.

33:53.840 --> 33:55.120
May the truth

33:56.600 --> 33:58.160
be revealed to the world.

34:24.600 --> 34:26.600
XIGU ALLEY

34:34.520 --> 34:36.679
TOFU

34:41.280 --> 34:42.760
Changyu.

34:44.360 --> 34:45.639
Changyu.

34:46.840 --> 34:48.639
My braid's crooked.

34:48.719 --> 34:50.400
Come here. Let me see.

34:51.520 --> 34:52.880
I'm here.

34:57.440 --> 34:58.360
Come.

35:01.680 --> 35:02.800
It's fine.

35:05.280 --> 35:06.680
Make do today.

35:06.760 --> 35:08.720
After I sell the pork,
I'll buy you sweets. Deal?

35:10.440 --> 35:11.440
Go get dressed.

35:12.560 --> 35:13.680
Careful.

35:22.640 --> 35:24.320
-Morning, Changyu.
-Morning.

35:24.400 --> 35:26.880
-Hard at work already?
-Morning, madam.

35:28.440 --> 35:30.280
-Morning, Changyu.
-Morning.

35:30.360 --> 35:31.720
-Morning.
-Morning.

35:31.800 --> 35:33.000
-Changyu.
-Morning.

35:33.080 --> 35:35.000
-Morning, Changyu.
-Morning.

35:46.200 --> 35:48.920
PORK

35:49.000 --> 35:50.040
Changyu,

35:50.120 --> 35:52.240
are you giving out
braised pig heart today?

35:53.280 --> 35:54.320
Not today.

35:54.400 --> 35:56.240
The pig heart is for sale now.

35:56.320 --> 35:58.200
We only gave it out on opening day.

35:58.280 --> 35:59.960
We won't be giving it away anymore.

36:00.040 --> 36:02.640
If you want some, it's 30 mace a <i>jin</i>.

36:04.200 --> 36:07.120
The other stall
gives braised offal free with meat.

36:07.200 --> 36:09.520
Why are you charging?

36:09.600 --> 36:10.760
Which stall?

36:11.760 --> 36:12.800
Guo the butcher's.

36:12.880 --> 36:14.800
Buy meat, get braised offal.

36:14.880 --> 36:16.880
Buy meat, get braised offal!

36:16.960 --> 36:18.160
Those cuts look fresh.

36:19.880 --> 36:22.560
Come, take a look!
Buy meat, get braised offal.

36:23.160 --> 36:24.600
So, are you giving it or not?

36:24.680 --> 36:26.800
If not, I'll go there.

36:28.840 --> 36:30.000
Of course we'll give.

36:30.960 --> 36:32.440
Then I'll stay.

36:32.520 --> 36:34.040
Two <i>jin</i> of shoulder.

36:36.640 --> 36:38.320
Mrs. Tao, your meat.

36:39.560 --> 36:42.040
-And here's your braised pig heart.
-All right.

36:47.200 --> 36:48.560
Here you go, miss.

36:48.640 --> 36:49.920
-Your meat.
-Thanks.

36:50.000 --> 36:52.080
That Guo is slippery.

36:52.160 --> 36:53.720
Told you not to give freebies,

36:53.800 --> 36:55.320
then started doing it himself.

36:56.600 --> 36:58.560
His cousin works as a clerk
at the county yamen.

36:58.640 --> 36:59.840
Watch yourself.

37:00.880 --> 37:02.720
-I will.
-Look at that meat. Fine, isn't it?

37:02.800 --> 37:04.040
Go buy from Fan's.

37:04.120 --> 37:05.400
Her lean cuts are redder,

37:05.480 --> 37:06.360
and her braise smells better.

37:06.440 --> 37:07.840
This looks half-dead.

37:07.920 --> 37:10.680
-Hey. What did you say?
-Come on, it's over there!

37:10.760 --> 37:12.560
You think their braise is liquid gold?

37:13.720 --> 37:15.280
Good thing you're back.

37:17.080 --> 37:20.040
Let's see how long he can keep handing out

37:20.120 --> 37:21.720
those salted scraps!

37:22.920 --> 37:25.320
Talking about me, are you? Fine.

37:26.120 --> 37:28.680
We'll see.

37:29.600 --> 37:31.480
Mrs. Yin, where's my noodles?

37:32.000 --> 37:32.880
What's the rush?

37:32.960 --> 37:34.040
You're not on the gallows.

37:34.120 --> 37:35.760
-They're coming!
-I am hungry.

37:36.880 --> 37:37.840
Hurry up.

37:38.440 --> 37:39.960
Changyu, I'm heading back.

37:40.040 --> 37:42.080
If that Guo gives you trouble again,

37:42.160 --> 37:43.880
tell me. I'm not afraid of him.

37:43.960 --> 37:45.320
Neither am I.

37:46.480 --> 37:47.320
See you.

37:47.840 --> 37:50.120
-How much do you need?
-Two <i>jin</i>.

37:50.200 --> 37:52.120
-Make mine two as well.
-All right.

38:28.680 --> 38:31.400
Foolish bird. Fell for such a crude trap.

38:41.520 --> 38:42.680
Up you go.

38:54.040 --> 38:54.920
Fly.

39:02.240 --> 39:04.960
WU AND QI HAVE ARRIVED
AT LIN'AN'S FOUR SEASONS BOOKSHOP

39:13.000 --> 39:13.840
Hurry up.

39:14.680 --> 39:17.160
While Changyu is out,
search the place thoroughly.

39:17.840 --> 39:19.360
Check outside. See if anyone's around.

39:19.960 --> 39:21.200
-All right.
-I'll check upstairs.

39:26.400 --> 39:27.400
The back courtyard's clear.

39:33.560 --> 39:34.760
Kitchen's empty.

39:39.560 --> 39:40.920
Nothing upstairs either.

39:50.280 --> 39:52.080
<i>Now's not the time to complicate things.</i>

39:52.600 --> 39:54.720
<i>There's nothing valuable here anyway.</i>

39:54.800 --> 39:55.640
Listen.

39:56.240 --> 39:57.880
If we don't find that land deed today,

39:57.960 --> 39:58.920
we're finished.

39:59.520 --> 40:00.480
Search properly.

40:01.000 --> 40:01.840
Understood.

40:11.200 --> 40:13.680
INTEGRITY, PRUDENCE, DILIGENCE

40:13.760 --> 40:15.960
You seem busy today.

40:16.040 --> 40:17.920
I won't keep you long.

40:18.000 --> 40:20.600
About the property transfer…
Could I trouble you--

40:20.680 --> 40:21.520
Say no more.

40:22.480 --> 40:24.920
Your uncle
has already submitted his petition.

40:25.440 --> 40:27.000
Court will convene in ten days
at the latest.

40:27.080 --> 40:28.800
You'd best be ready.

40:31.400 --> 40:32.400
There's something else.

40:32.920 --> 40:34.480
On my wedding day,

40:35.040 --> 40:36.640
please come early and join us for wine.

40:37.840 --> 40:38.920
All right, Changyu.

40:39.440 --> 40:40.680
You move fast.

40:41.280 --> 40:42.600
Congratulations in advance.

40:42.680 --> 40:43.600
I'll be there.

40:43.680 --> 40:44.840
YAMEN

40:44.920 --> 40:46.680
There's another favor I'd like to ask.

40:47.360 --> 40:51.520
My husband's silver and travel papers
were taken by bandits.

40:51.600 --> 40:53.560
He's about to marry into my family.

40:53.640 --> 40:55.200
I'd like to help him
reissue a travel pass.

40:55.920 --> 40:58.360
With the authorities
cracking down on refugees,

40:58.440 --> 41:00.600
getting new papers now won't be easy.

41:01.560 --> 41:02.960
But your father once helped me greatly.

41:03.560 --> 41:05.200
I'll see it done.

41:06.400 --> 41:07.640
Thank you, Mr. Wang.

41:07.720 --> 41:09.480
Good thing you're at the yamen.

41:09.560 --> 41:10.480
Think nothing of it.

41:10.560 --> 41:12.000
Consider it my gift to you.

41:14.520 --> 41:16.120
Check up there carefully.

41:43.000 --> 41:43.920
Found it!

41:44.960 --> 41:45.880
Over here.

41:47.320 --> 41:48.240
HAVE A FULL MEAL

41:48.840 --> 41:50.000
Over here!

41:50.080 --> 41:51.160
Look at this.

41:51.240 --> 41:53.440
She stuffed it behind that wall hanging.

41:53.520 --> 41:55.240
Had me tearing the place apart.

41:56.600 --> 41:58.560
Damn. Finally got it.

41:58.640 --> 41:59.720
All right.

41:59.800 --> 42:01.280
-Let's go.
-Stop.

42:07.880 --> 42:08.920
Where did this one come from?

42:09.000 --> 42:10.520
-Did you see him?
-You didn't notice him?

42:16.480 --> 42:17.600
Put the deed down.

42:19.040 --> 42:19.880
What did you say?

42:19.960 --> 42:21.400
I said,

42:22.040 --> 42:23.680
leave the land deed,

42:24.640 --> 42:26.120
and you can walk out of here.

42:28.960 --> 42:31.040
A cripple trying to play hero?

42:31.120 --> 42:32.880
He's lame.

42:32.960 --> 42:34.440
You're a cripple.

42:34.520 --> 42:35.800
You can barely stand straight.

42:35.880 --> 42:37.440
And you think you can fight?

42:38.600 --> 42:40.840
Believe me, I'll break that good leg too.

42:41.560 --> 42:42.600
Go on.

45:38.000 --> 45:41.560
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

45:41.640 --> 45:42.520
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
